name: Internet Usage details
query:
select
    site as "TCIL Code",
    udise_code as "UDISE Code",
    siteschool_name as "School Name",
    district as "District",
    block as "Block",
    pin_code as "Pin code",
    date as "Date",
    internet_service_provider as "Internet service provider",
    data_usage as "Data Usage (Gb)",
    monthly_bill_amount as "Monthly Bill Amount"
from `tabInternet consumption Record`;
